                    text: "The most documented issues are hydraulic lifter failure, VVT solenoid clogging, intake carbon buildup, and oil leaks from valve covers or the rear main seal. These are confirmed in GM service bulletins and field reports. Lifter issues are most common in pre-2006 models; VVT and intake problems arise from poor maintenance or extended oil intervals.",
