                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "Yes. The L33 responds well to tuning. ECU reprogramming can safely increase output by 20–30 kW, especially by optimizing AFM and VVT tables. Supporting mods like cold-air intakes, exhaust systems, and headers further enhance performance. However, aggressive tuning without upgraded internals or cooling can risk lifter or ringland damage, especially on older engines.",
