                    text: "The LF1 delivers smooth performance and good durability when properly maintained. Early models (2012-2014) had concerns with intake carbon buildup, but post-2015 revisions improved PCV system efficiency. Well-maintained examples can exceed 250,000 km. Regular oil changes with GM dexos1 5W-30 and periodic intake cleaning greatly enhance longevity.",
